In [39]:
def getwindowBorders(secondNumber, windowSize, samplingRate):
    window_start = 0
    window_end = 500
    window_start= (secondNumber-1)*window_end
    window_end= window_start+int(window_end*windowSize)
    return window_start, window_end
print(getwindowBorders(4, 1, 500))

        return (df[len(df)/2] + df[(len(df)/2)+1])/2
    return df['ECG'][int((len(df)/2)+0.5)]
